Workgroup Library
</p></td></tr>
<tr><td valign=top align=center>
<table width=1 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 align=left class=screenshotmarginleft><tr><td align=left><img class=screenshot width=640 height=480 src='pics/tutorials/newwave40/41.png'></td></tr></table>
</td><td valign=top style='padding-bottom: 3em;'>
<p>
NewWave makes it easier to share and access
information anywhere on a network. You don&rsquo;t need
to remember complex networking commands to get
vital information.
</p></td></tr>
<tr><td valign=top align=center>
<table width=1 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 align=left class=screenshotmarginleft><tr><td align=left><img class=screenshot width=640 height=480 src='pics/tutorials/newwave40/42.png'></td></tr></table>
</td><td valign=top style='padding-bottom: 3em;'>
<p>
The Workgroup Library works like a real library,
making it easy for you to see what information
is available on each network server.
</p></td></tr>
<tr><td valign=top align=center>
<table width=1 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 align=left class=screenshotmarginleft><tr><td align=left><img class=screenshot width=640 height=480 src='pics/tutorials/newwave40/43.png'></td></tr></table>
</td><td valign=top style='padding-bottom: 3em;'>
